dc_title_s: Addresses Fond du Lac County, WI 2015
dc_description_s: This point data layer represents street addresses for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Fond_du_Lac_Addresses_2015.gdb.[The fire address layer depicts fire address locations in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.Last published: May 21, 2015.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download
